title: League Winners And Disappointments In 2021
description:
Field Yates, Matthew Berry, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp recap MNF, discuss some league winners and disappointments from this season and tell you which players they're high on heading into 2022. Plus, a preview of some potential nominees for the 2021 Fantasy Focus Awards.
